{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abd03cbe0f","title":"“肃反从中央就错了”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"263c638b6d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"abd03cbe0f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"167ba6e3e1","name":"傅锟"},{"id":"7d0a44a770","name":"王佐堂"},{"id":"7d7fef83de","name":"华荫桐"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"a81160210d","name":"陆伟文"},{"id":"c7835dd180","name":"陈炳昕"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7927157ca6","type":"title","text":"“肃反从中央就错了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"fd390dcee2","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院陈炳昕王佐堂傅锟华荫桐陆伟文","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"129ee8f464","type":"paragraph","text":"陈炳昕说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"5eae7bf124","type":"paragraph","text":"「党中央按百分之五反革命来进行肃反，数字太大了，从中央就错了。我院党委是利用正确的口号来做坏事，按百分率斗，整了一百五十人，只有一个反革命，肃反打击人太狠，太不人道了。要求公开档案。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"64b776dfe9","type":"paragraph","text":"王佐堂说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"2f53464659","type":"paragraph","text":"「罗瑞卿的报告中提出肃反人数有百分之五要肃的，但肃反的结果与事实不符，如何解释？是否受到斯大林肃反扩大化的影响而提出这样数字。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"2232ee2be1","type":"paragraph","text":"傅锟说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"b6f7cd1a00","type":"paragraph","text":"「我院肃反机械执行百分之五比例，因而是扩大化了，搞错了。」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"175a8f8e43","type":"paragraph","text":"「对全院在肃反问题上的政策，我因不了解不能多说，但总的说做的不好，犯了相当严重的错误。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"bc6fa86326","type":"paragraph","text":"华荫桐说：「党的政策是不委曲一个好人，但我校委曲了一百多人。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"1ae0dc4fd1","type":"paragraph","text":"陆伟文说：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"60047f7aad","type":"paragraph","text":"「要看到人民对肃反的看法，看到肃反对人民的离心作用，说老实话，我就是说肃反之后不再相信共产党了，和共产党两条心。」","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"},{"id":"0d9dac85ae","type":"paragraph","text":"「用做十间房子的材料盖起一间房子，是否能说成绩是主要的？」","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f"}],"page":{"id":"573b9fbd78","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abd03cbe0f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}